        "were labelled as PAL or NTSC even though technically the discs carry neither PAL nor NTSC encoded signal. CCIR 625/50 and EIA 525/60 are the proper names for these standards; PAL and NTSC on the other hand are methods of encoding colour information in the signal.       Both the PAL and the NTSC system use a ": null
